{"tid":1469520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再話民意無用、唔好再話尋晚輸左","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:18:16.000Z","uid":124452,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d81d6d3a8048d0c7e5140613e6969967ffd6a596","tid":1469520,"uid":124452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:05:45.000Z","msg":"唔好再話民意無用，無民意你做乜都係錯。唔好再話要歸一早歸晒邊，要黃一早黃。「人道立場」係良知問題，同政治無關。民意要凝聚，唔聚就會散。<br />\n<br />\n勇武冷靜諗一諗，幾多人犧牲左都好，都仲有200萬人同你地一齊撐緊落去。「以眼還眼」係要對準政權<br />\n<br />\n不割席係勇武場合，勇武做乜，和理非都唔會割，會文宣返<br />\n<br />\n倒轉，和理非場合，勇武都要尊重返和理非，唔係唔比勇，但係要有底線，無底線同班狗有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n再話乜野前線決定，根本同一方獨大無分別。<br />\n<br />\n大家記住，和理非同勇武兩者要共存，缺一不可！互補長短！咁先係be water！<br />\n<br />\n尋晚一役係吸收經驗！唔好再問割唔割，互相尊重，就打死都唔撚割！"},{"pid":"14adccab139855859ea3f25e5d29304d8690c87b","tid":1469520,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:06:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0319ee460d96f434bc2d321c0bab04f05f617083","tid":1469520,"uid":124452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14adccab139855859ea3f25e5d29304d8690c87b","tid":1469520,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:06:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:09:52.000Z","msg":"多謝補充，唔好比啲二打六搞到失去焦點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141fe709e30018b2d6d65d557b6cade765ddc747","tid":1469520,"uid":31706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:15:07.000Z","msg":"前線係最易俾鬼煽動同帶動情緒<br />\n所以一定要互相提點<br />\n唔好俾分化撚得逞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe44f4586c0c7b36465a0d622ab731355c3ad8